      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior is essentially flawless, with no scratches, dents, or rust, and the paint retains full gloss and color with no fading. The interior is pristine, with no stains, tears, or excessive wear on any surfaces. Mechanically, the vehicle runs well with no known issues. All features and systems function as intended.",
