      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is the definition of turn-key perfection. Presenting in flawless condition inside and out, every surface, stitch, and system reflects meticulous care from day one. The paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish with zero blemishes, the interior is spotless and odor-free, and all mechanical components perform with the confidence of a car fresh off the showroom floor. Full service records available. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that truly lives up to the word 'mint' \u2014 no compromises, no surprises.",
